    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't find another one like this. I've babied this car since day one, and it's basically in showroom condition\u2014seriously, it still looks and feels brand new! It drives like a dream and is absolutely spotless inside and out. I\u2019m sad to let it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it. Feel free to reach out if you want to take a look!",
      "price": 44900.0,
