    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade 2004 Honda S2000 AP2, an analog masterpiece in collector-tier condition. This specimen retains its original F22C1 high-revving power plant, delivering linear power through the VTEC crossover. The chassis maintains total structural integrity with all 10 original factory VIN tags present. Mechanically, the 6-speed close-ratio transmission provides crisp, short-throw engagement, paired with a perfectly calibrated Torsen limited-slip differential. The double-wishbone suspension remains tight, providing the precise turn-in and neutral handling characteristic of this platform. Meticulously maintained with zero modifications, this is a rare opportunity to acquire a pristine example of Honda\u2019s engineering pinnacle.",
      "price": 49500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Mint condition. Clean title. Garage kept. No accidents. Service records available.",
      "price": 43000.0,
